videos.description: Kentucky's Tyler Ulis is way in the backcourt, but that doesn't stop him from throwing up a perfect lob to Alex Poythress for the alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: Kentucky with the alley-oop from way downtown

videos.description: Off of a missed free throw, Kentucky gets the rebound and passes it out to Tyler Ulis, who lobs it to Marcus Lee for the dunk without the ball hitting the floor once.
videos.headline: Kentucky has no need for dribbling to score alley-oop

videos.description: Alex Poythress has 21 points and 13 rebounds as No. 5 Kentucky defeats Eastern Kentucky 88-67.
videos.headline: No. 5 UK rebounds with 88-67 win over Eastern Kentucky
